-- DocKind.dhall
-- Classification of documentation

< Reference     -- API reference, module docs
| Guide         -- Conceptual guide, tutorial
| Cookbook      -- Recipe-based examples
| Spec          -- Formal specification
| Runbook       -- Operational procedures
| BestPractice  -- Prescriptive do/don't guidance
| Pattern       -- Reusable design/architecture pattern
| Notes         -- Internal notes, observations
| Other : Text
>
